<L>__{interior ramon's room day}
<A>__{ramon is still playing violin as concepcion and roberta enter. when he sees roberta he straightens up even more.}
<C>__{concepcion}
<D>__{roberta wants to talk to you, o.k.?}
<A>__{he nods. concepcion touches his head, then exits.}
<C>__{ramon}
<D>__{did that sound o.k.?}
<C>__{roberta}
<D>__{yeah, it did.}
<A>__{ramon smiles, pleased with himself.}
<C>__{roberta}
<D>__{i've been thinking about justin. remember how mad i got the last time i saw him?}
